sections.heading: tax; limitation.It shall be the duty of the county board of each county to cause to be annually levied and collected taxes authorized by law for county purposes
sections.text: The levy shall be subject to the limit established by section 77-3442.SourceLaws 1879, ยง 25, p. 361;Laws 1887, c. 27, ยง 1, p. 352;Laws 190
